avaya所有的宣告與保留音樂都以號碼存在，規劃dial plan時請注意留夠充足系統號碼區間

change media-gateway 1                                          Page   2 of   2
                             MEDIA GATEWAY 1

                                 Type: g450

Slot   Module Type            Name                    DSP Type  FW/HW version
 V1:   S8300                  ICC MM
 V2:   MM710                  DS1 MM
 V3:
 V4:
 V5:   MM717                  DCP MM
 V6:   MM711                  ANA MM
 V7:
 V8:                                                Max Survivable IP Ext: 8
 V9:   gateway-announcements  ANN VMM

請注意V9，衆所周知G450只有8個slot，V9作爲一個虛擬槽位存語音，需要自己手動添加

enable announcement-board 2v9

enable filexfer                                                 Page   1 of   1


                                 ENABLE FILE TRANSFER

                    Login: avaya
                 Password:
         Reenter Password:
                   Secure? n
            Board address: 2v9

基本只要注意secure？改爲n
賬號密碼全部自定義，後續ftp使用

add announcement 4402                                           Page   1 of   1

                       ANNOUNCEMENTS/AUDIO SOURCES

  Extension: 4402                            COR: 1
  Annc Name: hello                            TN: 1
  Annc Type: integrated                    Queue? y
     Source: 2v9
  Protected? n                              Rate: 64

add announcement 4403                                           Page   1 of   1

                       ANNOUNCEMENTS/AUDIO SOURCES

  Extension: 4403                            COR: 1
  Annc Name: holdOnMusic                      TN: 1
  Annc Type: integ-mus                     Queue? b
     Source: 2v9
  Protected? n                              Rate: 64

4402作爲一般宣告語音用，4403作爲保留音樂，名稱必須與ftp到g450中的檔案一致，當然你也可以用功能碼錄音，詳見FAC/Announcement Access Code
音檔格式：wav,16bit,8000hz,mono



















